### API Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:28472/api
@token = admin123

### 1. Login (Optional, just to verify password)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Import some test cookies
POST {{baseUrl}}/cookies/import
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "name": "session_id",
    "value": "123456789",
    "domain": "example.com",
    "path": "/",
    "expires": 1700000000,
    "httpOnly": true,
    "secure": true,
    "sameSite": "Lax"
  }
]

### 3. List all domains with cookie counts
GET {{baseUrl}}/cookies
Authorization: {{token}}

### 4. Export all cookies
GET {{baseUrl}}/cookies/export
Authorization: {{token}}

### 5. Export cookies for a specific domain search (LIKE query)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cookies/export?domain=example
Authorization: {{token}}

### 6. Get cookies for exact domain
GET {{baseUrl}}/cookies/example.com
Authorization: {{token}}

### 7. Delete cookies for a specific domain
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cookies/test.com
Authorization: {{token}}
